Ing '''Sidon''', o '''Saïda''', ([[Arabic language|Arabo]] '''{{lang|ar|صيدا}}''' ''{{transl|ar|Ṣaydā}}''; [[Phoenician language|Phoenician]] <span dir="rtl">[[File:phoenician sade.png|12px|צ]][[File:phoenician daleth.png|12px|ד]][[File:phoenician nun.png|12px|ן]]</span> ''Ṣydwn'', [[Greek language|Griego]] '''׃יה‏ם''', [[Hebrew language|Hebreo]] '''צידון''' ''Ṣīḏōn'', {{lang-tr|Sayda}}) ing katlung pekamaragul a lakanbalen o ciudad king in [[Lebanon]]. Atiu king [[:en:South Governorate, Lebanon|South Governorate]] ning Lebanon, king bebe dayatmalat ning [[:en:Mediterranean Sea|Mediterraneo]], manga 40&nbsp;km (25 mi) king [[pangulu]] ning [[Tyre, Lebanon|Tyre]] at 40&nbsp;km (25 mi) king [[mauli]] ning tungku o capitolio ning bangsa, ing [[Beirut]]. Ing lagiu na mangabaldugan yang ''pipandakpan asan''. Metung yang lakanbalen a maki 200,000 a memalen, a keraklan Muslim a [[Sunni]] o [[Shiite]], ampong Cristianong [[:en:Greek Catholic|Griego Catolico]] ampong [[Maronite]].

